     <p><b><u><a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/display/Library/Interlibrary+Loan+Policies" target="_new">Interlibrary Loan Policies</a></u></b> </p>
     <p><b>First Time User Registration for Interlibrary Loan</b> </p>
     <p>To request an item through Interlibrary Loan, you must first identify yourself to the library's ILLiad system. <b>If you have not used ILLiad before you must register in the ILLiad system, one time only, before you can place a request.</b> Logon on with your Drew Username and Password in the form above, fill in the brief registration form, and click the "Submit Information" button to register. </p>
     <p><b><u><a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/display/Library/Interlibrary+Loan+Policies#InterlibraryLoanPolicies-RenewingitemsthroughILLiad" target="_new">Renewals - How to renew your items.</a></u></b> </p>
     <p>Remote User Library Request Service: <b><u><a href="https://uknow.drew.edu/confluence/display/Library/Interlibrary+Loan+Policies#InterlibraryLoanPolicies-RemoteUsersLibraryRequestProgram%28DocumentDelivery%29" target="_new">(what is it?)</a></u></b> </p>
     <ul> 
      <li>Please indicate "remote user" in the note field of the request form. </li>
